         <abstract>
            <p>In this paper a numerical algorithm is proposed for the computation of the Fourier Transform. The quadrature rule developed is based on the Whittaker Cardinal Function expansion of the integrand and a certain Conformal Map. The error of the method is analyzed and numerical results are reported which confirm the accuracy of the quadrature rule.</p>
          </abstract>
